{"type":"message","id":"8ce24663","parentId":"4cd0d0e5","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:11:53.061Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n2mf3lkjuynv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783480313060}}
{"type":"message","id":"7b5869b4","parentId":"8ce24663","timestamp":"2026-07-08T03:11:58.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's 11:11 on Wednesday, July 8, 2026 - this is within the morning work hours (9:30-11:30). Let me check the rules:\n\n1. 喝水提醒: 10:30附近 - it's 11:11, not near 10:30\n2. 久坐提醒: 连续工作超过2小时 - I don't know how long they've been working\n3. 周五 17:00 附近: Not Friday\n\nThe heartbeat error message says \"搜索 旅游攻略 出错\" - this seems to be from a previous search that failed. The user might be expecting me to do something about this.\n \nThe exec failure from the dawn-can session shows an error code when trying to search for travel guides. Since it's a heartbeat and not an explicit user request, I should just acknowledge everything's okay rather than taking action on the failed search."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783480313061}}
